<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog Page 📝</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff9f0;
            color: #333;
            padding: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .post {
            background: #f1f8e9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .post h2 {
            color: #388e3c;
        }

        .post p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        a.btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a.btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Our Blog 📝</h1>
        <p>Latest thoughts, tips, and updates from our team 💡</p>

        <div class="post">
            <h2>🌱 Why We Love Fresh Fruits & Veggies</h2>
            <p>Eating fresh is not only healthy but also supports local farmers and the environment. We explore the benefits of going green and how you can start today!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="post">
            <h2>🚀 Building with Express.js</h2>
            <p>Express makes backend development smooth and fun. Learn how we structure our apps and keep things simple using EJS and clean routing.</p>
        </div>

        <a href="/product" class="btn">🛒 Explore Our Products</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
